present participle of 1510;
being:--be, come, have.

W)NE/OMAI ὠνέομαι ōnéomai   o-neh'-om-ahee
middle voice from an apparently primary  ὦνος ōnos,  (a sum or price);
to purchase (synonymous with the earlier 4092):-- buy.
